answers.body_markdown:
Since `foods` is an `ArrayList` you can just use the [`add(int, E)`][1] method to add an element at the beginning, like this:

```
public void addFoodFirst(String foodName) {
  foods.add(0, foodName);
}
```


  [1]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/ArrayList.html

